Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.35,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}掘塵封過往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:49.48,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}只為填罪業汪洋
